          <td>${esc(p.date)}</td>
        </tr>`).join('');

      resultsHTML += `
        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
          <h3 style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:14px;">📋 Permits (${matchedPermits.length})</h3>
